"Test del operador &

"1. Escalar simple
P = 600 kN
P & N
P & kN

"2. Momento (unidad compuesta)
M = 80 kN*m
M & N*mm
M & kN*m
M & kN*cm

"3. Presion
E = 200000 MPa
E & N/mm^2
E & kN/m^2
E & Pa

"4. Rigidez Winkler
k = 50000 kN/m^3
k & N/mm^3

"5. Vector con unidades mixtas via &
v = [600 kN; 80 kN*m]
v & [N; N*mm]

"6. Rigidez de resorte
k_s = 500 kN/m
k_s & N/mm

"7. F = k * u con &
u = 20 mm
F_r = k_s*u
F_r
F_r & kN
F_r & N

"8. Sistema K*u = F
K_m = [1000; -500|-500; 1500] kN/m
F_m = [10; -5] kN
u_m = lsolve(K_m; F_m)
u_m
u_m & [mm; mm]
u_m | [mm; mm]
